    EdgeLabelFormat.connectAccordingToLabel(DiffNode child, DiffNode parent, String edgeLabel)
    Adds the given child node as the child of the given parent node for all times described by the given label (via addChild(DiffNode, Time)) In particular, this method checks if the given edge label starts with LineGraphConstants.BEFORE_PARENT, LineGraphConstants.AFTER_PARENT, or LineGraphConstants.BEFORE_AND_AFTER_PARENT and connects both nodes accordingly.
